# EVASION GT - Cloudflare Pages Redirects Configuration

# Redirect www to non-www
https://www.evasion-gt.com/* https://evasion-gt.com/:splat 301

# SPA fallback - if a request doesn't match any static file, serve index.html
/* /index.html 200

# Cache control headers for static assets
/css/* 200
/js/* 200
/images/* 200

# No cache for HTML files
/*.html 200
